Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟巢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一共在孵五个蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四个孵化了  还剩下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想弄来吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在关注啦  老师你就想着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来客人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？没人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的确是在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这不是确实写着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这是只有我们才看得见的那一类东西
